SALES IN 2013 INCREASED 3.2 PERCENT, LED BY INDUSTRIAL AT 6.5 PERCENT, HEALTH CARE AT 3.8 PERCENT, AND SAFETY AND GRAPHICS AT 3.4 PERCENT. SALES INCREASED 1.1 PERCENT IN CONSUMER AND DECLINED 1.2 PERCENT IN ELECTRONICS AND ENERGY. TOTAL COMPANY ORGANIC L

